      <li class="tabs-title <% if(tab === 'DNA damage and Heart disease'.replace(/\s/g, '_')) { %> is-active <% } %> tab-center"><a class='my-reserach-tabs' href="#panel2c">Understanding the role of DNA damage in driving post-mitotic tissue aging</a></li>
      <li class="tabs-title <% if(tab === 'Genotoxic stress response in post-mitotic cells'.replace(/\s/g, '_')) { %> is-active <% } %> tab-last"><a class='my-reserach-tabs' href="#panel3c">How old are you? No really.</a></li>
